<h2>Secondary Categories: How Many and Which Ones</h2>
<p>Google allows up to 9 secondary categories. But more is not always better.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="GBP optimal category count vs average map ranking" src="/images/blog/gbp-categories-optimal-count.webp" /></p>
